				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Triggers once per nearby player by entering the voicebark trigger near the blood aquarium in the Moonrise Colony kitchen & dissection room.\r\nIf the player has visited the bloodbath section of the Oubliette before, a different branch will play. To test this flow, use ReCon command \"oe Oubliette_Enter\" and teleport out into the Colony kitchen."
				},
